➜湖北诗人朱翠荣（清美玉洁）：花溅泪
http://www.sohu.com/a/438177370_100115135	30300
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20201214/97a68ca68af746388c625666a8209679.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>花溅泪</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/朱翠荣（武汉）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">我想起一朵花被撕裂</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">穿过雨的过程</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">握不住雾水，哗啦哗啦滴流</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">洗白碎瓣</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">过滤纯度的疼痛</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">像一把剑刺穿夜梦心脏</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">痛得喧响</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">用力按不住伤口渗血</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">夜幕包裹着，你怎么能看见</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">花溅泪沉寂到夜海</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>写于2020年12月14日上午</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20201214/6f292e7cf9fa40eabbf134f08e546a06.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
