➜韩志华：南京大屠杀纪念日感怀（新韵）
http://www.sohu.com/a/438185006_100115135	32331
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201214/e3d32b7901824398ab66b5a762a31ffb.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>南京大屠杀纪念日感怀（新韵）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/韩志华</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">史册翻开滚泪珠，同胞卅万掉头颅。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">魂惊地狱阎王恨，血染神州妇幼哭。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">大罪难消都去审，深仇牢记共来诛。</p>
