➜河南诗人王琦伟：五绝·落叶（外一首）
http://www.sohu.com/a/438185591_100115135	32613
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20201214/d1ac9809b7e24c48a05822178611ea41.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>五绝·落叶（中华新韵）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/梦回桃花源（王琦伟）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一夜冷霜来，千枝叶老衰。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">化身成粪土，护养万花开。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>2020.12.13</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20201214/bb5f1873c0804f558ab7d5412064d173.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>五绝·柿子（中华新韵）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/梦回桃花源（王琦伟）</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">红柿似灯悬，身知畅月寒。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">天公银被赠，大爱暖开颜。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>2020.12.14</strong></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
